OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FBoris Johnson's ethics     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fadviser Lord Geidt quits   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Boris Johnson's ethics adviser Lord    
OL,6, Geidt has resigned after saying there  
OL,7, was a "legitimate question" over       
OL,8, whether the PM had broken ministerial  
OL,9, rules over Partygate.                  
OL,11,FHe said he was leaving the role, which 
OL,12,Fhe took up in April last year, "with   
OL,13,Fregret".                               
OL,15,FLord Geidt did not give a reason for   
OL,16,Fhis departure but in a statement he    
OL,17,Fsaid it was the "right thing" to do.   
OL,19,FIt comes a day after he spoke of       
OL,20,F"frustrations" with the PM's actions.  
